Hospital Management System API
------------------------------------

A simple Hospital Management System built using Django and Django REST Framework. This project demonstrates real-world ForeignKey-based relational database design and REST API development.

Features
-----------

1 Department Management
2 Doctor Management (linked to Department)
3 Patient Management
4 Appointment Scheduling (UUID primary key)
5 Prescription Management
6 Soft Delete support
7 Common audit fields (created_at, updated_at)

Database Relationships
-------------------------

Department → Doctor → Appointment → Prescription
Patient → Appointment

Tech Stack
-------------

Python
Django
Django REST Framework
MySQL
Git

Setup Instructions
----------------------

1) Clone Repository

    git clone https://github.com/Srinivasan-P-K/Hospital-Management-System-API-.git
    cd hospital-management-api

2) Create Virtual Environment

    python -m venv venv
    venv\Scripts\activate

3) Install Requirements

    pip install -r requirements.txt

4) Run Migrations

    python manage.py makemigrations
    python manage.py migrate

5) Start Server

    python manage.py runserver